Joel McHale https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joel_McHale 0 Joel Edward McHale (born November 20, 1971) is an American comedian, actor, writer, television producer, and television host. He is known for hosting The Soup and portraying Jeff Winger on the NBC/Yahoo! sitcom Community. He has appeared in the films Spy Kids: All the Time in the World (2011) and Ted (2012). He also starred in the short-lived CBS sitcom The Great Indoors. Joel_Edward_McHale ( born November_20 , 1971 ) is an_American_comedian , actor , writer , television_producer , and television_host .
